quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  19,77,"Naizvozvo wakambomuonawo here uyo akaramba kutenda mundima dzedu (Qur’aan rino) uye ndokuti: “Zvirokwazvo, ndichagachidzwa hupfumi nevana (kana ndikapihwa hupenyu zvekare)?”"
  19,78,Asi anoziva zvakavandika here kana kuti akatora chitenderano kubva kune vane ngoni zhinji (Allah)
  19,79,"Kwete! Tichanyora (pasi zvose) izvo zvaanotaura, uye tichawedzera murango wake chaizvo (mumoto weGehena)"
  19,80,"Tichagara nhaka (zvose) zvaanotaura (panguva yake yokufa vangave vana kana hupfumi hwatakamupa), uye achauya kwatiri ari oga (nemabasa ake chete)"
  19,81,"Uye vanotora vanamwari kunze kwaAllah (sezvinamatwa), kuti vavape rukudzo, nyembe nehukuru (uye vovadzivirira kubva kumurango waAllah)"
  19,82,"Kwete! (Asi izvo zvanamwari zvimudhori zvacho) zvicharamba kunamatwa kwazvona navo, uye zvichave zvinovapikisa (kureva kuti vanhu vanonamata zvimwe zvinhu zvisiri Allah, zvinhu izvozvo zvichavaramba pazuva rokutongwa)"
  19,83,Hauna kuona here kuti takatuma maShayaatween (vanadhiyabhorosi) kune avo vasingatendi (muna Allah) kuti vavasundire mukuita zvakaipa
  19,84,"Naizvozvo usave unovakurumidzira, zvirokwazvo, tiri kuvaverengera verengo (yamazuva eraramo yepasi pano uye tononotsa nguva yavo yokurarama yatakavatarira yokurarama kuti vawedzere kutadza kwavo)"
  19,85,Zuva (iro) ratichaunganidza avo vanotya Allah (Al-Muttaqqoon) kune (avo) vane ngoni zhinji (Allah) seWafd (vatumwa kubva pane vamwe)
  19,86,"Zvekare tichaendessa maMujrimoon (vaiti vemabasa akaipa, horomori) kuGehena, apo vanenge vaine nyota (semombe dzine nyota dzichienda kunonwa mvura)"
  19,87,Hakuna achazove nesimba rekureverera kunze kweuyo akatora (ane) chibvumirano nevane ngoni zhinji (Allah)
  19,88,"Uye vanoti: “(Allah) vane Ngoni Zhinji vane mwanakomana (sezvinotaura maJudha kuti Uzair (Ezra) mwana waAllah, uye maKristu vanoti Jesu (Isa) mwana waAllah, uyezve vasingatendi kubva kumaArab vanoti Allah vane vana vasikana (ngirozi nevamwe)).”"
  19,89,"Zvirokwazvo, mave munounza chinhu chakaipisisa (zvikuru)"
  19,90,"Apo matenga atova pedo pedo nekubvaruka nenyika yavakutobaduka (kutsemuka), uye makomo avakuda kutowondomoka kuti ave shopa (anoparara)"
  19,91,Nekuti vanonemera mwana kuna Ar-Rahmaan (vane Ngoni Zhinji)
  19,92,Uye hazvikodzeri kuti (Allah) vane Ngoni Zhinji vave (vanotora) vanoita mwanakomana (kana vana)
  19,93,Hakuna kana chii zvacho chiri mumatenga nemunyika asi kutoti chinouya kunaAr-Rahmaan (Vane Ngoni Zhinji) semuranda
  19,94,"Zvirokwazvo, (Allah) vanoziva mumwe nemumwe pakati pavo, zvakare (Allah) vave vanonyatsovaverenga verengo (yakazara)"
  19,95,Uye mumwe nemumwe wavo achauya pazuva rokumutswa kwavari (Allah) ari oga. (Asina kana mudziviriri kana mubatsiri)